# 💫 About Me:
I am a passionate and highly motivated aspiring MERN stack developer, currently focused on mastering front-end technologies including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. With a strong interest in building modern, responsive web applications, I am consistently working on real-world projects and enhancing my coding skills through hands-on practice. As I progress in my journey, I am gradually expanding my knowledge into backend technologies like Node.js, Express, and MongoDB, with the goal of becoming a full-stack web developer. Alongside technical growth, I am also committed to continuously learning core software engineering principles, version control, and best development practices to prepare for a successful career in the tech industry.<br><br>


